analysis: The documents primarily concern amendments, modifications, and revocations of previous executive orders, regulations, and instructions. They cover a range of topics including customs tariffs, foreign currency exchange rates for US employees abroad, citizenship regulations, shipping regulations, leave policies for Panama Canal employees, appointments to the Maritime Commission, Canal Zone regulations, consular fees, immigration regulations, and foreign service regulations. Many of the documents relate to the Panama Canal and its administration.
title: Amendments and Modifications to Existing Regulations and Orders
